, etc."},{"code":"H2820","text":"should asswage","lemma":"חָשַׂךְ","translit":"","pos":"verb","disp":0,"lit":"assuage","med":"assuage","tho":"forbear","range":"to restrain or (reflex.) refrain; by implication, to refuse, spare, preserve; to observe"},{"code":"H5205","text":"and the moving","lemma":"נִיד","translit":"","pos":"noun","disp":0,"lit":"moving","med":"moving","tho":"moving","range":"motion (of the lips in speech)"},{"code":"H6310","text":"my mouth","lemma":"פֶּה","translit":"","pos":"preposition","disp":0,"lit":"-ing to","med":"-ing to","tho":"after","range":"the mouth (as the means of blowing), whether literal or figurative (particularly speech); specifically edge, portion or side; adverbially (with preposition) according to"},{"code":"H8193","text":"of my lips","lemma":"שָׂפָה","translit":"","pos":"noun","disp":0,"lit":"band","med":"band","tho":"bank","range":"the lip (as a natural boundary); by implication, language; by analogy, a margin (of a vessel, water, cloth, etc.)"}],"div":[{"code":"H553","lemma":"אָמַץ","lit":"confirm","tho":"be courageous (of good courage"},{"code":"H1119","lemma":"בְּמוֹ","lit":"for","tho":"in into"},{"code":"H2820","lemma":"חָשַׂךְ","lit":"assuage","tho":"forbear"},{"code":"H6310","lemma":"פֶּה","lit":"-ing to","tho":"after"},{"code":"H8193","lemma":"שָׂפָה","lit":"band","tho":"bank"}],"struct":"contains a main verb; prepositional phrase(s); clause connector(s)"},"9":{"tokens":[{"code":"H639","text":"me in his wrath","lemma":"אַף","translit":"","pos":"noun","disp":0,"lit":"countenance","med":"countenance","tho":"face","range":"properly, the nose or nostril; hence, the face, and occasionally a person; also (from the rapid breathing in passion) ire"},{"code":"H2786","text":"me he gnasheth","lemma":"חָרַק","translit":"","pos":"verb","disp":0,"lit":"gnash","med":"gnash","tho":"gnash","range":"to grate the teeth"},{"code":"H2963","text":"He teareth","lemma":"טָרַף","translit":"","pos":"verb","disp":0,"lit":"catch","med":"catch","t